name: Smile, Sunshine 8x10" Signed Giclée Print
description:
Here it is, your daily reminder. No matter what you've got going on, there's always a reason to smile, sunshine. 

This is an 8x10" open edition Giclée print of my digitally designed piece, "Smile, Sunshine". Printed on matte paper with archival quality inks, the design isn't going anywhere. Each print has a thin white border for framing, and will be signed and titled in the bottom margin. It will be shipped in a bend-proof cardboard mailer and protected by a clear cellophane sleeve.

name: Chuting Stars 8x10" Signed Giclée Print
description:
Today I confess a great tragedy: Never in my life have I seen a shooting star. You're shocked and appalled, I know. As am I, for the most part, but such an unknown affords a certain artistic license—That which lent itself to my Chuting Stars.
